'''Force Body''' was a type of [[The Force/Legends|Force]] [[Force power/Legends|technique]] which allowed any [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]] to push their body's endurance past a safe limit, ignoring and sacrificing their health and well-being in order to sustain their connection to the Force. Very powerful connection to the Force was required for this ability's use. With this, Jedi could live through what would otherwise [[Death/Legends|kill]] them.

This ability could also be used to prevent the user from being severed from the Force. In addition, the ability shared similarities with [[Force valor]], [[Enhance Attribute]] and [[Battlemind]], as well as the dark side ability known as [[Force Enrage|Force rage]].

